videoDetails.Title: War Thunder's Forbidden Tank Lineup
videoDetails.Description:
Decal link: https://tinyurl.com/42thwzv3

A decent number of tanks in War Thunder are no longer accessible for a multitude of reasons, with the most famous being Panther II, Tiger II 10.5cm, and Coelian from the German tech tree. 

Check the channel "About" section for the link to the creator of my profile picture.
